"docs/asyncio/asyncio-part-1.html>`__"
msgstr ""
"`Tutorial de Python Asyncio <https://bbc.github.io/cloudfit-public-"
"docs/asyncio/asyncio-part-1.html>`__"

#: ../../source/development/xinference_internals.rst:163
msgid ""
